subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: The Jayhawks beat the Buffaloes in a tournament opener on Colorado’s home court. Earlier, Creighton won its first game in the N.C.A.A. women’s tournament since 1994, defeating Syracuse.
